border: 1px solid #d0e6be;
border-radius: 4px;">
    <h1>JUST ADDED</h1><h2>Now you can post to Pinterest and Wordpress (as well as Facebook)!</h2>
</div>

    <div style="padding-top:40px;padding-bottom:20px;" class="row one-column cf ui-sortable section" id="le_body_row_1" data-style="eyJwYWRkaW5nVG9wIjoiNDAiLCJwYWRkaW5nQm90dG9tIjoiMjAifQ==">
        <div class="fixed-width">
            <div class="one-column column cols" id="le_body_row_1_col_1"><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_1_col_1_el_1"><div class="element"> <h2 style="font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#4d4d4d;text-align:center;margin-bottom:20px;"></h2><h2 style="text-align: center;">It's Time To Turbo Charge Your Facebook&nbsp;Pages!</h2>

                    </div></div><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_1_col_1_el_2"><div class="element"> <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;color:#696969;text-align:center;line-height:33px;margin-bottom:40px;">You no longer need to spend hours looking for the best viral content for your&nbsp;Facebook pages. Postradamus does most of the work for you in seconds.</h2>
                    </div></div><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_1_col_1_el_3"><div class="element"> <div class="op-custom-html-block">
                            <div style="text-align: center"><div class="sbo-video-container"><iframe width="853" height="480" src="//www.youtube.com/embed/Lhe73zB5b-s?rel=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div>
                        </div>
                    </div></div><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_1_col_1_el_4"><div class="element"> <div style="text-align:center"><a href="#access" class="button-style-3"><img src="files/get-instant-access.png" alt=""></a></div>
                    </div></div><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_1_col_1_el_5"><div class="element"> <ul class="feature-block feature-block-style-icon feature-block-with-icon feature-block-two-col cf">
                            <li><div><span class="feature-block-icon-container"><img class="feature-block-icon" src="files/67.png"></span><h2>Search for content</h2><p>Find images from places like Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, Pinterest and Imgur.&nbsp;Copy in the URL of any web page and scrape the images. Also find books and products from Amazon (affiliate link included right in the text). Find news stories from Reddit or RSS feeds. Add YouTube videos. Mass upload your own images from your hard drive.</p>

                                </div></li>

                            <li><div><span class="feature-block-icon-container"><img class="feature-block-icon" src="files/84.png"></span><h2>Create Lists</h2><p>Create huge lists of viral content (photos, text, videos, links). Search, schedule, manipulate and copy posts from one list to another. Randomize your list schedule times and then publish straight to Facebook.</p>

                                </div></li>

                            <li><div><span class="feature-block-icon-container"><img class="feature-block-icon" src="files/86.png"></span><h2>Schedule Your Lists</h2><p>Create one or more schedules that you can then use on your lists to automatically choose dates and times for each post in your list. When you setup your schedule, you can choose multiple times of the day for each day of the week you want your posts to be published on Facebook. Built in calendar for drag and drop manual scheduling as well.</p>

                                </div></li>

                            <li><div><span class="feature-block-icon-container"><img class="feature-block-icon" src="files/10.png"></span><h2>Export to Facebook, Pinterest, Wordpress</h2><p>Export your lists to Facebook via various methods. Use the Facebook API for a one click immediate schedule to Facebook. Or, use a method which requires iMacros and controls your browser for you, posting manually to Facebook. Export your list to a CSV file and have an assistant manually schedule posts for you.</p>

                                </div></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div></div></div></div></div>
    <div style="background:#f0f0f0;border-top-width:1px;border-bottom-width:1px;border-style:solid;border-top-color:#ebebeb;border-bottom-color:#ebebeb;" class="row one-column cf ui-sortable section" id="le_body_row_2" data-style="eyJiYWNrZ3JvdW5kQ29sb3JTdGFydCI6IiNmMGYwZjAiLCJib3JkZXJXaWR0aCI6IjEiLCJib3JkZXJDb2xvciI6IiNlYmViZWIifQ==">
        <div class="fixed-width">
            <div class="one-column column cols" id="le_body_row_2_col_1"><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_2_col_1_el_1"><div class="element"> <h2 style="font-style:normal;font-weight:300;text-align:center;margin-bottom:20px;">Just a few reasons to make Postradamus start working for you!</h2>
                    </div></div><div class="element-container cf" data-style="" id="le_body_row_2_col_1_el_2"><div class="element"> <ul class="feature-block feature-block-style-1 feature-block-three-col cf">
                            <li><div>
                                    <img class="feature-block-1" src="files/27.png"><h2 style="font-size:21px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;"><span>Save Countless Hours</span></h2><p style="font-family:&quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif;color:#707070;">Spending less time&nbsp;looking for content and manually scheduling it to Facebook means you have more time to do&nbsp;the important things in life.</p>

